t transport vehicles to be delivered to the army would be lowered. To avoid `` price drifts and financial approximations'' on major programs a new external auditing system will be in place in the autumn, <PERSON> Rocard </PERSON> said. It will be jointly directed by an army controller and an inspector of finance and will be able to call on private auditing agencies.
