<HEAD>Hong Kong Residents Demand That Chinese Leaders Quit</HEAD>
<HEAD>With AM-China, Bjt</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By CINTY LI</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>HONG KONG (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
