<FIRST>a a AM-ReligionRdp Adv09   06-07 0593</FIRST>
<SECOND>AM-Religion Rdp, Adv 09,0616</SECOND>
<HEAD>$Adv09</HEAD>
<HEAD>For Release Fri AMs, June 9 and Thereafter</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
